comment3.text=\n\ STATE\ 0\:\ Eases\ toward\ the\ target\ X\ using\ proportional\ interpolation.\n\ Plays\ the\ battle-cry\ voice\ on\ the\ first\ frame.\n\ Transitions\ to\ STATE\ 1\ when\ close\ enough\ to\ the\ target.\n
